Cursor
 Tailwind v4  switched  from cursor: pointer to cursor: default for the button component.  If you want to keep the cursor: pointer behavior, add the following code to your CSS file: 

src/styles.css
@layer base {
  button:not(:disabled),
  [role="button"]:not(:disabled) {
    cursor: pointer;
  }
}

